<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PodStream - High Quality Podcast Recording Platform</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #7c4dff;
            --primary-dark: #5e35b1;
            --secondary: #2d3748;
            --light: #f7fafc;
            --dark: #1a202c;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: var(--dark);
            color: white;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        .background-video-container {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .background-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 32, 44, 0.7), rgba(26, 32, 44, 0.9));
            z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .background-video {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .logo svg {
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        nav ul li {
            margin-left: 2rem;
        }
        
        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
        }
        
        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid white;
        }
        
        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .hero {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .features-grid {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background-color: rgba(45, 55, 72, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .feature-card h3 svg {
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        .feature-card p {
            color: #cbd5e0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .start-button {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .start-button .btn {
            padding: 1rem 3rem;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
        
        .note {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #a0aec0;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }
            
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            nav {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="background-video-container">
        <div class="background-overlay"></div>
        <video id="bgVideo" class="background-video" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
            <source src="./videoplayback (1).mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12C2 17.52 6.48 22 12 22C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2ZM12 8C13.1 8 14 8.9 14 10C14 11.1 13.1 12 12 12C10.9 12 10 11.1 10 10C10 8.9 10.9 8 12 8ZM12 18.2C10.23 18.2 8.64 17.43 7.6 16.15C7.66 14.73 10.64 14 12 14C13.35 14 16.34 14.73 16.4 16.15C15.36 17.43 13.77 18.2 12 18.2Z" fill="#7c4dff"/>
                </svg>
                PodStream
            </a>
            
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">Log in</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Start for Free</a>
            </div>
        </header>
        
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Create professional podcasts with a single click</h1>
            <p>Your online studio to connect with guests, record in high quality, and share your voice with the world. No complicated setup required.</p>
            
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M12 14C13.66 14 15 12.66 15 11V5C15 3.34 13.66 2 12 2C10.34 2 9 3.34 9 5V11C9 12.66 10.34 14 12 14ZM11 5C11 4.45 11.45 4 12 4C12.55 4 13 4.45 13 5V11C13 11.55 12.55 12 12 12C11.45 12 11 11.55 11 11V5ZM17 11C17 13.76 14.76 16 12 16C9.24 16 7 13.76 7 11H5C5 14.53 7.61 17.43 11 17.92V21H13V17.92C16.39 17.43 19 14.53 19 11H17Z" fill="#7c4dff"/>
                        </svg>
                        Connect with WebRTC
                    </h3>
                    <p>See and hear your guests in real-time with crystal clear quality, no lag, and minimal setup.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12C2 17.52 6.48 22 12 22C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2ZM12 4C16.42 4 20 7.58 20 12C20 16.42 16.42 20 12 20C7.58 20 4 16.42 4 12C4 7.58 7.58 4 12 4ZM9 16H15V10H11V14H9V16Z" fill="#7c4dff"/>
                        </svg>
                        High-Quality Recording
                    </h3>
                    <p>Record locally in pristine quality, regardless of your internet connection. Never lose your best moments.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M14 2H6C4.9 2 4 2.9 4 4V20C4 21.1 4.9 22 6 22H18C19.1 22 20 21.1 20 20V8L14 2ZM16 16H8V14H16V16ZM16 12H8V10H16V12ZM13 9V3.5L18.5 9H13Z" fill="#7c4dff"/>
                        </svg>
                        Simple Collaboration
                    </h3>
                    <p>Share a link and your guests are in. No downloads or accounts required for them to join.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M17 10.5V7C17 6.45 16.55 6 16 6H4C3.45 6 3 6.45 3 7V17C3 17.55 3.45 18 4 18H16C16.55 18 17 17.55 17 17V13.5L21 17.5V6.5L17 10.5Z" fill="#7c4dff"/>
                        </svg>
                        One-Click Recording
                    </h3>
                    <p>Start and stop recording with a single click. Focus on your content, not on technical complexities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="start-button">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Start Recording Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const video = document.getElementById('bgVideo');
        const startTime = 20; 

        video.addEventListener('loadedmetadata', () => {
            video.currentTime = startTime;
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>